text: I've also seen it work out the other way around too. UCSB alum have found there ways all over and into so many fields too, which gets some of those little bonus points for shared experience. Honestly, in my experience, the party school rep really only applies to people who live in CA. I never hear about it now that I live on the East Coast.
I made chicken pho last weekend and planning to make beef pho now that I got the bones. The beef one is about 16 hours.
